snippet.title: WRC Generations - Hybrid Cars Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-order the game: https://wrcthegame.com/

Rally1 Hybrid cars are here! Experience driving sensations with much greater engine torque, delivering up to 30% more power when accelerating. Drivers must also think about their strategy before the start of the stages to optimize the management of electrical power and the battery. 

WRC Generations is the most successful title in the series to date and notably contains the most extensive list of cars and tracks ever offered.

#WRCGenerations will be available November 3, 2022 on PC, PlayStation®4, PlayStation®5, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S and later on Nintendo Switch.
